Invocation Name: the music quiz
des:
The Music Quiz has now transformed into Song Quiz, a thrilling music trivia game that tests your knowledge of popular songs from the past 60 years. Guess the correct title and artist to earn points, and compete against music fans across the country in live head-to-head challenges.

With Song Quiz, you can explore a wide variety of playlists featuring pop music from every decade, including the 2010s, 2000s, 90s, 80s, 70s, and 60s. New music is added regularly, ensuring that you always have fresh challenges to enjoy.

If you have any issues or feedback, please email us at support@volleythat.com. We'd love to hear from you and help make your Song Quiz experience even better!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
